31#include "gmp.h"
32#include "gmp-impl.h"
33
34void
35mpf_mul (mpf_ptr r, mpf_srcptr u, mpf_srcptr v)
36{
37 mp_srcptr up, vp;
38 mp_size_t usize, vsize;
39 mp_size_t sign_product;
40 mp_size_t prec = r->_mp_prec;
41
42 usize = u->_mp_size;
43 vsize = v->_mp_size;
44 sign_product = usize ^ vsize;
45
46 usize = ABS (usize);
47 vsize = ABS (vsize);
48
49 up = u->_mp_d;
50 vp = v->_mp_d;
51 if (usize > prec)
52 {
53 up += usize - prec;
54 usize = prec;
55 }
56 if (vsize > prec)
57 {
58 vp += vsize - prec;
59 vsize = prec;
60 }
61
62 if (usize == 0 || vsize == 0)
63 {
64 r->_mp_size = 0;
65 r->_mp_exp = 0; /* ??? */
66 }
67 else
68 {
69 mp_size_t rsize;
70 mp_limb_t cy_limb;
71 mp_ptr rp, tp;
72 mp_size_t adj;
73 TMP_DECL;
74
75 TMP_MARK;
76 rsize = usize + vsize;
77 tp = TMP_ALLOC_LIMBS (rsize);
78 cy_limb = (usize >= vsize
79 ? mpn_mul (tp, up, usize, vp, vsize)
80 : mpn_mul (tp, vp, vsize, up, usize));
81
82 adj = cy_limb == 0;
83 rsize -= adj;
84 prec++;
85 if (rsize > prec)
86 {
87 tp += rsize - prec;
88 rsize = prec;
89 }
90 rp = r->_mp_d;
91 MPN_COPY (rp, tp, rsize);
92 r->_mp_exp = u->_mp_exp + v->_mp_exp - adj;
93 r->_mp_size = sign_product >= 0 ? rsize : -rsize;
94
95 TMP_FREE;
96 }
97}
